summary: fixes the double chairs and the backwards chest and other errors in Proudspire Manor
descriptionHtml:
This is an ESP file made with Creation Kit that fixes the double chairs on the second floor, the wall clipping behind the mannequins in the basement and the backwards chest in the master bedroom. It also adds a second chest to the left of the enchanting table in the basement.

If you find an error I missed feel free to leave a comment and i will try to fix it as soon as possible
author: Awl393
